ir veyst UNK gartl? KHAGORA.

00:13:23.886 --> 00:13:24.960
azoy...

00:13:24.004 --> 00:13:25.415
un oyfn kop?

00:13:25.388 --> 00:13:29.350
oyfn kop bin ikh gegangen a kapl mit a HAT.

00:13:26.029 --> 00:13:27.810
vos hot ir getrogn oyfn kop?

00:13:31.142 --> 00:13:33.127
ir hot getrogn peyes?

00:13:31.851 --> 00:13:35.222
ikh gey haynt oykh, kh'gey haynt oykhet a kapl mit a...

00:13:33.893 --> 00:13:36.840
ir hot getrogn pey- ir hot getrogn peyes?

00:13:35.222 --> 00:13:36.991
yo, SURE.

00:13:39.445 --> 00:13:41.510
ober dos iz alts far der krig.

00:13:41.672 --> 00:13:45.749
vi azoy hot ayer heym oysgezen? ir gedenkt ayer adres?

00:13:45.891 --> 00:13:50.610
⟨i-⟩, d-, v- Mitskevitsher, nayn un tsvontsik, ⟨b-⟩

00:13:51.561 --> 00:13:52.905
in Rayshe.

00:13:52.860 --> 00:13:55.166
vi azoy hot ayer heym oysgezen?

00:13:55.138 --> 00:13:56.566
a khsidishe heym.

00:13:56.623 --> 00:13:58.844
dertseylt mir fun der khsidisher heym.

00:13:58.395 --> 00:14:00.189
di khsidishe heym

00:14:00.189 --> 00:14:05.898
hot gev- hot ge- ⟨iz er⟩, er iz geven a beker, der tate. er hot ge- UNK eygene bekeray ho'mir gegat.

00:14:06.175 --> 00:14:07.401
un,

00:14:07.609 --> 00:14:15.500
un, nokh dem iz gevorn a fayer in m- undzer bekeray, un m'hot gebroykht tsu, ⟨⟩, m'hot ge- s'hot gekost gelt, al-...

00:14:14.663 --> 00:14:16.665
vu iz geven di bekeray?

00:14:16.485 --> 00:14:18.980
bekeray iz geven bay der ban gas.

00:14:20.383 --> 00:14:23.009
ober vi azoy hot ayer heym oysgezen?

00:14:22.240 --> 00:14:24.020
⟨a⟩ khsidishe heym!

00:14:23.252 --> 00:14:27.923
dertseylt mir vi zi hot oysgezen: dray, vifl tsimern iz geven, vu m'iz geshlofn,

00:14:26.695 --> 00:14:33.940
o, o. tsimer- tsimern, tsimern iz gevezn nisht azoy fil vi, vos, ⟨m'- m'iz⟩ in Amerike.

00:14:27.923 --> 00:14:29.844
vu m'hot gegesn. ⟨dertseyln⟩...

00:14:33.940 --> 00:14:37.033
tsimern bay undz, ⟨ze'mir⟩ geven zibn kinder,

00:14:37.275 --> 00:14:40.458
un eltern, iz shoyn nayn gevezn.

00:14:40.802 --> 00:14:44.220
nu, mir hobn gehat dra-, dray ROOMS.

00:14:45.409 --> 00:14:49.971
es zenen nisht geven k- s'iz nisht geven, azoy vi me zogt, ⟨felder⟩; s'iz geven a s- plats UNK.

00:14:49.971 --> 00:14:51.540
s'iz geven ⟨d-⟩ ot dos iz

00:14:51.540 --> 00:14:54.397
⟨d- d-⟩ gevezn, d⟨o-...⟩ mir ho'mir gevoynt

00:14:54.927 --> 00:14:56.102
un THAT'S ALL.

00:14:56.014 --> 00:14:56.630
..

00:14:56.720 --> 00:15:03.124
 nokh dem hot er khasene gemakht a tokhter, nokh dem hot men khasene gemakht a zun, un nokh dem hot men khasene gemakht nokh a tokhter.

00:15:03.124 --> 00:15:06.783
s'iz gevorn veyniker, ober m'hot gevoynt in der zelber voynung.

00:15:07.617 --> 00:15:10.412
mit vemen hot ir geshlofn in a tsimer?

00:15:10.806 --> 00:15:11.795
vemen?

00:15:11.295 --> 00:15:13.381
ver iz geshlofn in a tsimer mit aykh?

00:15:12.660 --> 00:15:14.380
⟨i- a- i-⟩ mit mir?

00:15:13.820 --> 00:15:14.990
ye.

00:15:14.380 --> 00:15:21.390
a-, ven, ven ikh bin geven take k- nokh, a... kleyn ken ikh dokh nisht zogn, vayl ikh bin nokh haynt oykhet kleyn,

00:15:21.390 --> 00:15:25.860
 nor vos den? ⟨s-⟩ bin yung gevezn, bin ikh geshlofn mitn tatn,

00:15:26.297 --> 00:15:30.071
un di shvester, di yingere shvester, geshlofn mit der mame.

00:15:30.718 --> 00:15:32.399
un, d⟨o-⟩...

00:15:31.596 --> 00:15:33.710
un vu zenen di andere geshlofn?

00:15:33.081 --> 00:15:37.243
nu, a COUCH, un tsvey, nokh tsvey betn in a ROOM.

00:15:37.384 --> 00:15:39.420
azoy hot men dokh gelebt in der heym.

00:15:39.493 --> 00:15:44.144
in velekhn tsimer in der heym zent ir ammeystn geven ven ir zent geven in der heym?

00:15:44.083 --> 00:15:45.764
ven kh'bin geven in der heym?

00:15:45.805 --> 00:15:47.925
bin ikh geven ammeystn in der KITCHEN.

00:15:48.707 --> 00:15:49.850
in der KITCH-

00:15:49.024 --> 00:15:50.024
far vos?

00:15:49.850 --> 00:15:55.350
in der KITCHEN, vayl m'hot dokh gegesn,. dort iz geven... nokh dem bin ikh aroysgelofn oyfn,

00:15:55.350 --> 00:15:56.970
in droysn aroys.

00:15:58.495 --> 00:16:03.562
dertseylt mir fun a yontev in der heym. velekhn yontev hot ir ammeystn lib gegat?

00:16:03.388 --> 00:16:04.664
shvues.

00:16:05.008 --> 00:16:06.820
dertseylt mir fun shvues.

00:16:06.257 --> 00:16:10.253
shvues hot men, hot men dokh mekabl geven di toyre.

00:16:10.253 --> 00:16:13.895
m'hot dokh gegebn di toyre tsu di yidn un shvues iz gevorn.

00:16:14.290 --> 00:16:18.470
iz, ⟨g-⟩ hot men gegat CHEESECAKE tsu esn.

00:16:18.470 --> 00:16:23.550
UNK geven kinder dokh, UNK geven, kh'veys, ikh bin geven alt ts- a tsen yor.

00:16:23.550 --> 00:16:28.323
nu, ⟨un mir ze'mir⟩ gegangen, m'hot arumgev- -yogt zikh, un THAT'S, THAT'S ALL vos ikh...

00:16:28.988 --> 00:16:32.930
un m'hot gegesn CHEESECAKE, m'hot gegesn dos, m'hot gelebt.

00:16:33.004 --> 00:16:37.217
ver hot gebakn dem CHEESECAKE? di mame, tsi der tate in der bekeray?

00:16:36.750 --> 00:16:39.120
⟨in der, der⟩ bekeray, di shvester,

00:16:39.282 --> 00:16:42.448
di tsveyte eltste shvester fun der ⟨d-⟩ eltster.

00:16:42.707 --> 00:16:46.680
zi iz geven, zi hot gearbet afile in a bekeray oykhet.

00:16:46.926 --> 00:16:48.790
zi hot gekent arbetn.

00:16:49.170 --> 00:16:51.847
ir hot a mol geholfn oykh in der bekeray?

00:16:52.039 --> 00:16:58.440
nisht, ven ikh bin gevezn tsen yor alt, ober shpeter, yo, hob ikh geholfn, ⟨yo⟩.

00:16:55.313 --> 00:16:56.842
ober shpeter?

00:16:58.266 --> 00:17:00.251
vos hot ir getun dortn?

00:16:59.700 --> 00:17:01.240
kh'hob gearbet.

00:17:01.240 --> 00:17:05.279
ikh, un ikh arbet, ⟨, nisht do,⟩ ikh hob dokh gearbet do in a bekeray oykhet,

00:17:05.791 --> 00:17:07.033
in Amerike.

00:17:07.580 --> 00:17:09.498
ir arbet yetst in a bekeray?

00:17:08.863 --> 00:17:13.150
n- ikh arbet shoyn nisht, fun nayn un akhtsik,

00:17:13.200 --> 00:17:14.645
UNK akht yor.

00:17:15.968 --> 00:17:18.341
vos hot men gebakn in der bekeray?

00:17:18.145 --> 00:17:22.440
in der bekeray hot men gebakn R- ROLLS, beygl,

00:17:22.440 --> 00:17:26.590
un, z-, runde, runde zeml,

00:17:26.590 --> 00:17:30.520
farshidene zakhn. m'hot ger- -arbet r- un milekh-rogelekh.

00:17:30.767 --> 00:17:34.518
⟨s'iz⟩ farshidene zakhn. s'iz geven zibn, zibn m- minim

00:17:34.518 --> 00:17:36.970
iz gevezn, zibn maykholim azelekh⟨n⟩,

00:17:37.129 --> 00:17:40.170
vos m'hot gekent, a beker hot aroysgebakn.

00:17:39.913 --> 00:17:42.489
vifl mentshn hobn gearbet in der bekeray?

00:17:42.192 --> 00:17:46.135
⟨in⟩, bay undz?, bay undz hot men gearbet... tate,

00:17:46.849 --> 00:17:51.320
un der bruder vos iz dokh gesh- ersht do do geshtorbn,

00:17:51.557 --> 00:17:54.048
un i- un ikh hob tsugeholfn.

00:17:57.210 --> 00:17:59.330
ir zent gegan in shule?

00:17:59.438 --> 00:18:02.250
in shule? yo, in, nisht in der poylisher.

00:18:02.940 --> 00:18:04.781
ir zent gegan in a poylisher shule?

00:18:03.893 --> 00:18:06.064
NO, nisht in der poylisher.

00:18:05.817 --> 00:18:07.954
in avoser shule zent ir gegan?

00:18:07.437 --> 00:18:09.287
kh'bin gegangen in der yidisher.

00:18:09.630 --> 00:18:12.762
dertseylt mir vi azoy s'hot oysgezen di yidishe shule.

00:18:11.773 --> 00:18:15.179
s'hot oysgezen aza oremkeyt, azoy vi

00:18:15.179 --> 00:18:23.006
 UNK ir veyst dokh, az d- az der UNK der GOVERNMENT helft nisht tsu, iz groyse tsores.

00:18:22.725 --> 00:18:24.845
vos hot men gelernt dortn?

00:18:24.970 --> 00:18:27.725
poylish, m- redn poylish,

00:18:27.725 --> 00:18:30.100
un m'hot ge- m'hot gelernt,

00:18:30.100 --> 00:18:31.983
THAT'S ALL. vos hot men gekent lernen?

00:18:32.125 --> 00:18:35.426
in bloyzn kop hot men nisht gekent geyn tsishn di goyishe.

00:18:35.550 --> 00:18:39.220
az m'iz geven in der goyisher shil, un dos, hot men dokh in ⟨ka- ke-⟩...

00:18:39.220 --> 00:18:41.732
zey hobn dokh gemuzt geyn in bloyzn kop, un do,

00:18:41.732 --> 00:18:49.560
un, ⟨un s'iz⟩ di tslom- di tseylems, s'iz dokh geven arum un arum di sh-, der shCHOOL UNK. ⟨lozt mikh⟩ geyn in bloyzn kop azoy?

00:18:49.560 --> 00:18:51.317
iz men nisht gegangen.

00:18:51.317 --> 00:18:56.300
nor iz geven a yidishe shule, nor ⟨vo-⟩ di yidishe shule hot ⟨z-⟩ dokh nisht gekent oyshaltn keyn sakh.

00:18:57.977 --> 00:18:59.788
iz es, m'hot ⟨mikh ge-⟩

00:18:59.788 --> 00:19:03.253
m'hot zikh, m'hot geshtupt azoy v- vos ⟨me ken⟩, veyst dokh...

00:19:02.247 --> 00:19:05.852
m'iz gegan, yingelekh mit meydelekh tsuzamen?

00:19:05.892 --> 00:19:11.640
yingelekh mit meydelekh zenen nisht gegangen tsuzamen, nor yinglekh mit meydlekh zenen yo gegangen.

00:19:12.253 --> 00:19:18.983
UNK s'iz geven fareynen, s'iz geven der Shoymer, Hashomer Hatsair, s'iz geven UNK Bney Akive UNK iz gevezn.

00:19:18.983 --> 00:19:21.010
⟨s'iz dokh fa-⟩ farshidene UNK...

00:19:20.033 --> 00:19:25.157
un a yidishe, un a khasidishe mishpokhe hot erloybt aykh tsu geyn tsuzamen mit,

00:19:25.213 --> 00:19:28.649
mit meydlekh? NO, dort iz nisht ge- dos nisht.

00:19:25.551 --> 00:19:27.148
mit meydlekh in shul?

00:19:28.791 --> 00:19:30.960
meydlekh zenen gegangen SEPARATE.

00:19:31.305 --> 00:19:32.548
in shule

00:19:32.250 --> 00:19:33.054
yo.

00:19:32.605 --> 00:19:34.928
zenen meydlekh gegan bazunder?

00:19:34.798 --> 00:19:36.648
yo, zikher!

00:19:37.026 --> 00:19:39.990
tomer ⟨in aza⟩ UNK vos gegangen tsuzamen,

00:19:40.182 --> 00:19:45.508
voltn zey dokh shoyn nisht geven, volt men dokh... azoy zikh gegangen peyes mit, mit hitlen, ⟨nor,⟩

00:19:45.683 --> 00:19:49.659
in a goyisher shul ⟨m- muzstu⟩ dokh oys⟨t⟩un dos hitl ineveynik.

00:19:49.429 --> 00:19:52.595
ober in der yidisher shule vu ir zent gegan,

00:19:52.602 --> 00:19:54.360
vu d-... ⟨yo⟩?

00:19:52.669 --> 00:19:55.475
zent ir, in der shule vu ir zent gegan,

00:19:55.150 --> 00:19:56.089
nu?

00:19:55.475 --> 00:19:58.754
iz men gegan yinglekh mit meydlekh ts- bazunder?

00:19:57.833 --> 00:19:59.680
yo, SURE.

00:20:02.018 --> 00:20:05.758
AND m'hot gelernt, avosere,

00:20:05.983 --> 00:20:07.732
PRZEDMIOTn hot men gelernt?

00:20:07.435 --> 00:20:10.669
vos, ⟨P-,⟩ PRZEDMIOTes? s'iz gevezn

00:20:10.776 --> 00:20:14.949
ge- gemore, s'iz geven Rashe, s'iz geven khumesh, s'iz ⟨dokh⟩ geven ales.

00:20:14.949 --> 00:20:19.446
kh'meyn, khumesh iz dokh, ⟨di⟩ Rashe kumt dokh tsu badaytung fun der khumesh.

00:20:19.446 --> 00:20:21.755
un azoy iz gevezn. un gemore.

00:20:24.158 --> 00:20:26.362
ir zent gegan in a yeshive?

00:20:26.622 --> 00:20:29.501
SURE! nu, vos, vos far a frage? zikher!

00:20:29.153 --> 00:20:32.454
di shule iz geven a yeshive, vu ir zent gegan?

00:20:31.431 --> 00:20:36.280
dos heyst a yeshive, yo, ⟨az-⟩ vi azoy iz haynt, do.

00:20:35.008 --> 00:20:37.331
vi azoy hot geheysn di yeshive?

00:20:37.506 --> 00:20:39.654
di yeshive hot gehey- vi hot zi geheysn?

00:20:39.654 --> 00:20:41.583
nisht gev- gehat keyn SPECIAL nomen;

00:20:41.657 --> 00:20:43.490
di yeshive iz di yeshive.

00:20:43.699 --> 00:20:47.670
nisht gehat keyn SPECIAL nomen. ⟨IF, IF⟩... nu, nu?

00:20:44.931 --> 00:20:46.376
vifl yor,

00:20:47.412 --> 00:20:50.038
vifl yor zent ir gegan in der,

00:20:50.415 --> 00:20:52.130
in der yeshive?

00:20:51.360 --> 00:20:56.840
biz kh'bin ⟨a⟩, oyfgeva-... oyfgevaksn bin ikh keyn mol nisht; ir zet vi UNK ir kent mikh zen,

00:20:56.840 --> 00:21:05.870
 nor ikh bin hekher ⟨gev- g-⟩ greber gevorn, hekher gevorn, un azoy bin ikh ⟨gev- ge-⟩ shoyn gelernt in besmedre-, in di kloyz.

00:21:06.008 --> 00:21:09.309
biz vifl yor zent ir gegan in der yeshive?

00:21:08.370 --> 00:21:12.540
in d- in di yeshive? NO, d- yeshive iz shoyn gevezn,

00:21:12.540 --> 00:21:15.232
vos m'hot shoyn gekent aleyn far zikh lernen,

00:21:15.897 --> 00:21:20.990
aleyn lernen gemor⟨UNK⟩ gemore, toysefes.

00:21:23.659 --> 00:21:29.272
biz vi- biz vifl yor zent ir gegan dortn? vi alt zent ir geven?

00:21:29.160 --> 00:21:33.910
ver, ikh? ⟨b- d- v-⟩ biz s'hot oysgebrokhn di krig,

00:21:34.645 --> 00:21:36.478
UNK nayn un draysik

00:21:37.041 --> 00:21:40.330
ze'mir dokh shoyn avekgelofn, ikh mitn bruder.

00:21:39.268 --> 00:21:41.256
far nayn un draysik,

00:21:40.922 --> 00:21:42.400
far nayn un d-...

00:21:41.256 --> 00:21:43.296
in der heym,

00:21:43.909 --> 00:21:47.480
vi azoy zenen di yidn durkhgekumen mit di nisht-yidn?

00:21:48.212 --> 00:21:51.733
nisht-yidn? undz ho'mir dokh ge-... ⟨vosere ge-⟩...?

00:21:50.693 --> 00:21:53.488
vi azoy zenen di yidn durkhgekumen mit di goyim?

00:21:54.760 --> 00:21:56.290
ikh farshtey nisht vos...

00:21:55.688 --> 00:22:00.086
vi azoy zenen di yidn in shtot durkhgekumen mit di goyim?

00:21:58.827 --> 00:22:07.174
nu, azoy, v⟨i ir⟩ veyst, ⟨,⟩ der, m'hot, vi azoy m'hot geshrign, "ŻYDZI DO PALESTYNY," ⟨"ŻYDZI UNK"⟩ farshidene, ⟨dos⟩, s'iz geven farshidns.

00:22:08.327 --> 00:22:12.050
vi azoy, ir hot gehat shkheynim vos zenen geven nisht-yidn?

00:22:12.090 --> 00:22:16.927
ye, ikh hob gegat, yo, mi⟨- ikh, i-⟩ mir hobn gevoynt bar a goy, bar a koval.

00:22:17.237 --> 00:22:18.440
ye?

00:22:17.845 --> 00:22:20.330
ir veyst vos s'meynt a koval, ha?

00:22:20.330 --> 00:22:26.440
m⟨UNK⟩ m'hot gegat ts- tsu tun mit ot d⟨e-⟩... er iz gevezn, er hot gekent yidish redn oykhet.

00:22:26.603 --> 00:22:29.870
er iz geven oykh in der estraykhisher krig mit, ⟨do-⟩...

00:22:30.045 --> 00:22:33.869
⟨iz,⟩ er hot, m'hot gevoynt dort bay im,

00:22:34.028 --> 00:22:35.304
bay dem koval.

00:22:36.610 --> 00:22:39.861
ir hot gehat nokh shkheynim vos zenen nisht geven yidn?

00:22:39.613 --> 00:22:43.112
dort? NO, dort iz geven, ze'mir ale geven yidn.

00:22:43.112 --> 00:22:47.606
⟨nu, a-⟩ nisht, eyner iz geven frimerer, un eyner iz gevezn a bisl

00:22:47.646 --> 00:22:49.530
avek fun frumkeyt.

00:22:51.780 --> 00:22:56.009
s'zenen geven a sakh yidn in Rayshe vos zenen geven avek fun frumkeyt?

00:22:55.611 --> 00:22:59.400
mer g- avek vi, vi frume.

00:22:59.520 --> 00:23:00.887
vi vayt avek?

00:23:01.180 --> 00:23:07.485
avek. er hot, ikh, gegangen sh- afile um shabes, er iz avekgegangen vos me,

00:23:07.542 --> 00:23:16.280
er hot nisht ge- er iz gegangen UNK vu er hot nor gevolt, gegangen in bloyzn kop, farshidene z⟨i⟩kh- zakhn; azelekhe zakhn hot gevezn in Rayshe oykhet,

00:23:16.280 --> 00:23:19.760
ober n- zenen nisht avekgegangen COMPLETE.

00:23:19.760 --> 00:23:23.519
er hot gever- -volt epes a bisl t⟨UNK⟩men un er zol zikh shemen,

00:23:23.519 --> 00:23:26.942
hot e- hot er gornisht getun um shabes, iz er geven bahaltn.

00:23:28.534 --> 00:23:31.700
tomer hot er get- epes ge- dos, iz er geven bahaltn.

00:23:34.542 --> 00:23:41.100
vos hot ir getun ⟨m-⟩ mit ayere fraynd in der f- ven ir hot gehat fraye tsayt? vos flegt ir tun?

00:23:40.954 --> 00:23:43.592
vos ikh fleg tun ven kh'hob gehat fraye tsayt?

00:23:43.592 --> 00:23:48.997
s'iz keyn mol nisht geven keyn fraye tsayt. m'hot eybik, oder UNK az m'iz in ⟨d-⟩ a moshl, UNK

00:23:49.071 --> 00:23:54.470
in AGE, s'iz ge- UNK s'iz geven in AGE shoyn, a e- der elter

00:23:54.470 --> 00:23:57.738
iz gevezn, veyst ir dokh vi azoy s'hot oysgezen:

00:23:57.930 --> 00:24:05.590
der iz, m'hot zikh gekhavert mit a bisl der, der iz gegangen tsuzamen mit d- mit an andern, mit UNK. m'- m'hot zikh ge⟨k-⟩

00:24:05.590 --> 00:24:09.807
a bisl nisht gelozt zikh g⟨el- gey-⟩ avekgeyn fun,

00:24:09.807 --> 00:24:13.240
fun COMPLE- fun, fun frumkeyt.

00:24:13.240 --> 00:24:15.870
er hot gevolt ⟨z-⟩ blaybn a yid.

00:24:15.295 --> 00:24:16.183
ver?

00:24:16.071 --> 00:24:19.710
der man, afile vos er iz a bisele shoyn gevezn

00:24:19.710 --> 00:24:21.383
ongerirt azoy UNK,

00:24:21.383 --> 00:24:24.390
hot er zikh oykhet geshemt tsu geyn,

00:24:24.390 --> 00:24:26.691
moshl, er zol geyn in bloyzn kop in der gas.

00:24:26.691 --> 00:24:29.784
do hot er zikh shoyn geshemt, hot er ba- geven bahaltn

00:24:30.212 --> 00:24:34.883
⟨in a⟩ baheltenish, er hot gegangen, me zol nisht zen, bay nakht, me zol nisht kenen...

00:24:34.883 --> 00:24:37.570
azoy UNK m'hot, m'hot gelebt.

00:24:37.671 --> 00:24:39.456
gelebt gants voyl.

00:24:39.456 --> 00:24:43.318
m'hot nisht gevust fun keyn krig un m'hot nisht gevust fun keyn,

00:24:44.590 --> 00:24:46.474
"ŻYD DO PALESTYNY."

00:24:47.796 --> 00:24:48.431
i⟨UNK⟩...

00:24:47.920 --> 00:24:50.541
m'hot nisht gevust fun keyn "ŻYD DO PALESTYNY?"

00:24:50.361 --> 00:24:54.846
UNK, s'iz geven a, a sakh vos zey hobn ge- geshrign, "Ż-

00:24:54.846 --> 00:24:56.480
ŻYDY DO PALESTYNY."

00:24:57.955 --> 00:24:59.468
ir zogt...

00:24:58.174 --> 00:25:01.160
ir kent, ir kent poylish, ha?

00:25:01.313 --> 00:25:02.353
ah...

00:25:03.878 --> 00:25:07.297
ir hot gevust vos se tut zikh in Doytshland?

00:25:07.740 --> 00:25:09.322
o, di letste tsayt?

00:25:09.008 --> 00:25:10.740
di letste tsayt.

00:25:09.548 --> 00:25:12.140
nu, SURE. z- zikher.

00:25:11.522 --> 00:25:13.051
vos hot ir gevust?

00:25:13.108 --> 00:25:14.590
vos kh'hob gevust?

00:25:14.590 --> 00:25:17.700
az zey traybn aroys di yidn fun Daytshnland.

00:25:17.445 --> 00:25:19.408
vi azoy hot ir dos gevust?

00:25:19.318 --> 00:25:27.479
s'zenen dokh gekumen fun Daytshnland, a sakh tsurik tsu, tsu P- Rayshe un tsu, un tsu andere shtet, tsu Kroke, tsu...

00:25:26.963 --> 00:25:30.804
dertseylt mir vos, ⟨,⟩ fun di doytshe yidn vos zenen gekumen keyn Rayshe.

00:25:30.574 --> 00:25:33.667
di doytshe yidn vos zenen gekumen keyn Rayshe,

00:25:33.667 --> 00:25:41.590
ni- iz m-, a bisl, s'iz nisht geven keyn groyse, dos... iz geven afile az di vos zenen a mol gevezn in D- in,

00:25:41.590 --> 00:25:45.502
in Rayshe, nor zenen avek keyn Daytshnland makhn parnose,

00:25:45.913 --> 00:25:49.265
UNK zenen dos, un yetst hobn zey dokh gemuzt tsurikgeyn.

00:25:49.474 --> 00:25:53.281
zey hobn dokh nisht gegat k- z-... a, ⟨vos er iz⟩ geven a daytsher,

00:25:53.440 --> 00:25:54.952
hot er dokh nisht gekent,

00:25:54.975 --> 00:26:01.350
UNK heysn UNK er hot dokh oykhet, er hot dokh aroysgeyogt, az yidn, m'hot dokh aroysgeyogt yidn fun Daytshnland.

00:26:01.540 --> 00:26:05.490
un, azoy iz m- iz gevorn be- erger.

00:26:04.594 --> 00:26:08.790
ir hot getrofn di yidn vos m'hot zey aroysgev- ⟨,⟩ - yogt fun Doytshland?

00:26:08.475 --> 00:26:10.430
SURE. zikher.

00:26:10.129 --> 00:26:11.793
vos hobn zey dertseylt?

00:26:11.715 --> 00:26:21.884
vos zey hobn dertseylt? zey hobn dertseylt az s'iz shlekht un zey vern, un zey, un di, me shlogt un me harget. s'iz dokh bald in akht un draysiker yor geven a gev- gantsn,

00:26:21.975 --> 00:26:26.780
gantse UNK ⟨u⟩n l- ⟨u⟩n lagers mit, alem, aroysgeyogt.

00:26:26.785 --> 00:26:29.816
ir hot gevust az s'iz do lagers in Doytshland?

00:26:29.704 --> 00:26:33.056
SURE. vos far a UNK frage? vos, zikher!

00:26:34.429 --> 00:26:36.735
vos hot ir gevust fun Hitlern?

00:26:36.977 --> 00:26:39.806
Hitler,? Hitler, yimakh-shemoy!

00:26:40.470 --> 00:26:42.995
er iz geven, m'hot ales ge-...

00:26:42.934 --> 00:26:44.835
ir hot demolt gevust?

00:26:44.200 --> 00:26:45.881
yo!

00:26:46.390 --> 00:26:49.440
yeder, az, az m⟨'iz,⟩ kumt, yene kumen tsurik,

00:26:49.498 --> 00:26:53.120
un me shlogt, me shl⟨a⟩⟨UNK⟩ men v- yogt aroys,

00:26:53.210 --> 00:26:55.568
⟨nu,⟩ farshteyt zikh, d⟨UNK⟩...

00:26:54.426 --> 00:26:56.681
ir hot gehat a radyo in der heym?

00:26:57.261 --> 00:26:59.195
neyn, SPECIAL nisht, NO.

00:26:59.573 --> 00:27:01.727
me fleg leyenen tsaytungen?

00:27:01.530 --> 00:27:04.117
tsaytungen, di, iz geven der Agude, nu,

00:27:04.117 --> 00:27:07.684
der Agude hot gegat aroysgegebn, er hot gegat UNK "Der Togblat,"

00:27:08.702 --> 00:27:11.025
hot er aroysgegebn der PAPER, yo.

00:27:10.491 --> 00:27:12.611
zey flegn shraybn derfun?

00:27:12.347 --> 00:27:15.620
SURE! vos far a frage? z- zikher!

00:27:18.118 --> 00:27:22.820
⟨tsi⟩ di yidn in Rayshe hobn moyre gegat az se geyt pasirn

00:27:22.911 --> 00:27:25.419
epes in Poyln? m'hot geredt derfun?

00:27:25.037 --> 00:27:27.258
m'hot moyre gegat far zey,

00:27:27.433 --> 00:27:30.582
nor m'hot nisht gevust az s'zol azoy pasirn.

00:27:31.585 --> 00:27:37.384
az s'zol zay- azoy pasirn hot men nisht gevust. m'hot gevust az, az s'iz shlekht bay zey.

00:27:37.710 --> 00:27:42.969
v- ⟨s'iz⟩ dokh ongehoybn nisht mit eyn mol tsu, tsu, aroystsuvorfn UNK di yidn.

00:27:43.009 --> 00:27:46.870
m'hot nor moyre gegat az s'vet epes kumen, vayl di, m⟨UNK⟩

00:27:46.870 --> 00:27:49.570
d- di vos zenen nisht geven in Daytshnland,

00:27:49.570 --> 00:27:53.955
nor vos zenen gekumen, vos m'iz arayn- z- vos zenen arayngeforn keyn Daytshnland,

00:27:54.113 --> 00:27:58.060
hobn, hot men gemuz- hobn, zenen zey ge- gemuzt tsurikforn.

00:27:58.652 --> 00:28:01.568
hobn zey shoyn nisht UNK... zey iz dokh shoyn geven biter,

00:28:01.568 --> 00:28:02.814
az ⟨eyner⟩...

00:28:02.972 --> 00:28:06.594
dort in Daytshnland hot yeder yid gemakht a gut lebn.

00:28:08.524 --> 00:28:10.318
vayl dor-, di daytshn

00:28:10.318 --> 00:28:12.765
hobn take gemakht parnose. zey hobn.

00:28:12.765 --> 00:28:17.532
zey hobn ge- zey hobn gelebt a gutn, arayng- aroysgegangen

00:28:17.532 --> 00:28:22.110
mit shnurbendlekh, tsi mit dem, farkoyfn. un m'hot gekoyft!

00:28:24.336 --> 00:28:29.580
vel'mir yetst dos endikn, un vel'mir geyn tsu der NEXTn teyl in a por minut.

00:28:29.490 --> 00:28:30.930
UNK
